Interview: Xinjiang is the frontline of combating terrorism | ENGLISH.JSCHINA.COM.CN
Let's go back to our reporter Wu Guoxiu in Urumqi, along with Professor Zheng Liang from Xinjiang University, to discuss the issue.
Q1. What are major measures in fighting terrorism in Xinjiang? And what are the biggest challenges?
Q2. During President Xi's visit to the US, he and President Obama agreed to step up intelligence sharing in fighting terrorism. What effect will this have for Xinjiang?
Q3. Terrorism inevitably makes headlines. How close is it actually in our life? How should we understand the fight against terrorism and the role of Xinjiang in it?